beer.beer_description:
Pan Pacific is brewed with golden syrup, suggestively named Golden Naked Oats and a combination of New Zealand Motueka and Australian Galaxy hops.

Pan Pacific is a rich red amber, with generous malt and fruit hop character, and a subtle hint of toasted coconut at the end of the palate. Itâ€™s a brew to meet the arrival of Autumn, with nice body and character with just a hint of warmer climes.

Come fly with us.
